# Project Structure
- Public entry is [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx)
- Detail page is [app/defects/[slug]/page.tsx](mdc:app/defects/[slug]/page.tsx)
- Admin routes under [app/admin](mdc:app/admin)
- API route handlers under [app/api](mdc:app/api)
- Prisma schema at [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
- DB client at [lib/db.ts](mdc:lib/db.ts)
- Auth helpers at [lib/auth.ts](mdc:lib/auth.ts)
- Validation schemas at [lib/validation.ts](mdc:lib/validation.ts)
- Storage types at [lib/storage/types.ts](mdc:lib/storage/types.ts) and local adapter at [lib/storage/local.ts](mdc:lib/storage/local.ts)
- Global styles at [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css)
